.SCENE 2.1 - 01:30-04:30 [Slide 6]

INT. GUNTUR MAIN BAZAR / MODERN RETAIL STORE - DAY

AUDIO:
Background: Light, engaging instrumental.
Voice: Female narrator (conversational, relatable, warm).
